          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2014-08-15T14:05:55Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Stopping Abusive Student Loan Collection Practices in Bankruptcy Act of 2014 - Amends federal bankruptcy law to allow an individual whose student loan debt is discharged due to undue hardship to recover the costs of, and a reasonable attorney's fee for, the discharge proceeding if the court finds that the position of the creditor was not substantially justified.</p>]]></text>
